c: 3
v: 45
t: "As the Angels said, \"O Maryam, (Mary) surely Allah gives you good tidings of a Word from Him whose name is the Masih Isa (Literally: pens) son of Maryam, esteemed in the present (life) (Literally: the lowly \"life\", i.e., the life of this world) and the Hereafter, and one of the near -stationed (i.e., stationed near to' Allah)"